description: mkdir -p /usr/local/go 	&& curl -SLO "http://resin-packages.s3.amazonaws.com/golang/v$GO_VERSION/go$GO_VERSION.linux-alpine-amd64.tar.gz" 	&& echo "cefdfd2b941303fd25dd06bd04871b12a58a2a9a3d105eb67aed40dac092c863  go$GO_VERSION.linux-alpine-amd64.tar.gz" | sha256sum -c - 	&& tar -xzf "go$GO_VERSION.linux-alpine-amd64.tar.gz" -C /usr/local/go --strip-components=1 	&& rm -f go$GO_VERSION.linux-alpine-amd64.tar.gz
pip install Flask dnspython oauth2client google-api-python-client httplib2 google-cloud
cd /home/dataplay3/client &&     mkdir /home/dataplay3/server/dataplay/static &&     npm install --silent &&     npm run build

set -ex; 	curl -o wordpress.tar.gz -fSL "https://wordpress.org/wordpress-${WORDPRESS_VERSION}.tar.gz"; 	echo "$WORDPRESS_SHA1 *wordpress.tar.gz" | sha1sum -c -; 	tar -xzf wordpress.tar.gz -C /usr/src/; 	rm wordpress.tar.gz; 	chown -R www-data:www-data /usr/src/wordpress
git clone --depth=1 https://github.com/jvm-profiling-tools/perf-map-agent     && cd perf-map-agent && cmake . && make

mkdir -p /usr/local/go 	&& curl -SLO "http://resin-packages.s3.amazonaws.com/golang/v$GO_VERSION/go$GO_VERSION.linux-armv7hf.tar.gz" 	&& echo "f8a06c2832ca01001d0ffc68a44a2d4c569285cd485a0a61ee7169bc87adbb0f  go$GO_VERSION.linux-armv7hf.tar.gz" | sha256sum -c - 	&& tar -xzf "go$GO_VERSION.linux-armv7hf.tar.gz" -C /usr/local/go --strip-components=1 	&& rm -f go$GO_VERSION.linux-armv7hf.tar.gz

export CHROMEDRIVER_RELEASE=$(curl --location --fail --retry 3 http://chromedriver.storage.googleapis.com/LATEST_RELEASE)       && curl --silent --show-error --location --fail --retry 3 --output /tmp/chromedriver_linux64.zip "http://chromedriver.storage.googleapis.com/$CHROMEDRIVER_RELEASE/chromedriver_linux64.zip"       && cd /tmp       && unzip chromedriver_linux64.zip       && rm -rf chromedriver_linux64.zip       && sudo mv chromedriver /usr/local/bin/chromedriver       && sudo chmod +x /usr/local/bin/chromedriver       && chromedriver --version

curl --silent --show-error --location --fail --retry 3 --output /tmp/google-chrome-stable_current_amd64.deb https://dl.google.com/linux/direct/google-chrome-stable_current_amd64.deb       && (sudo dpkg -i /tmp/google-chrome-stable_current_amd64.deb || sudo apt-get -fy install)        && rm -rf /tmp/google-chrome-stable_current_amd64.deb       && sudo sed -i 's|HERE/chrome"|HERE/chrome" --disable-setuid-sandbox --no-sandbox|g'            "/opt/google/chrome/google-chrome"       && google-chrome --version
